article_title: Hawaii is nation’s healthiest state, Mississippi its unhealthiest
article_text: Hawaii has the nation's healthiest residents in 2014 and Mississippi has the most unhealthy, according to the 25th annual America's Health Rankings released Wednesday by the United Health Foundation.
